 streets during the fall in Bar Harbor. Location: Maine (44.389° N 68.208° W) Status: Public domain. Photo by Dennis Adams","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Acadia_All_American_Road_-_Street_in_Bar_Harbor_-_NARA_-_7716800.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/38/Acadia_All_American_Road_-_The_Bubbles_on_Jordan_Pond_-_NARA_-_7716814.jpg/1280px-Acadia_All_American_Road_-_The_Bubbles_on_Jordan_Pond_-_NARA_-_7716814.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/38/Acadia_All_American_Road_-_The_Bubbles_on_Jordan_Pond_-_NARA_-_7716814.jpg","cap":"Acadia All American Road The Bubbles on Jordan Pond","desc":"Blue waters contrast against fall hills at the Bubbles on Jordan Pond. Location: Maine (44.334° N 68.256° W) Status: Public domain. Photo by Dennis Adams","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Acadia_All_American_Road_-_The_Bubbles_on_Jordan_Pond_-_NARA_-_7716814.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4d/Acadia_All_American_Road_-_Thompson_Island_Information_Center_-_NARA_-_7716797.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4d/Acadia_All_American_Road_-_Thompson_Island_Information_Center_-_NARA_-_7716797.jpg","cap":"Acadia All American Road Thompson Island Information Center","desc":"The Thompson Island Information Center is a cluster of small, weathered wood structures with an interpretive sign in front. Location: Thompson Island, Maine (44.427° N 68.366° W) Status: Public domain.","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Acadia_All_American_Road_-_Thompson_Island_Information_Center_-_NARA_-_7716797.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0d/Acadia_All_American_Road_-_Visitors_at_an_Acadia_Byway_Overlook_-_NARA_-_7716805.jpg/1280px-Acadia_All_American_Road_-_Visitors_at_an_Acadia_Byway_Overlook_-_NARA_-_7716805.jpg","full":"https://uploa